lead_paragraph: Germany kept their first clean sheet for nearly a year as they coasted to a 2-0 win over fellow Euro 2016 finalists Hungary on Saturday in the final warm-up friendly for both teams.

headline.print_headline: Germany Finally Keep Clean Sheet in Win Over Hungary
